<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About QuickBlog</h1>
    <hr>

    <!-- Project Overview Section -->
    <section class="my-4">
        <h2 class="text-primary-emphasis">What is QuickBlog?</h2>
        <p>QuickBlog is a dynamic blogging platform where users can create, edit, delete, and view blogs effortlessly. It is designed to be simple yet powerful, offering a seamless experience for sharing thoughts and ideas.</p>
    </section>
    <hr>

    <!-- Functionality Section -->
    <section class="my-4">
        <h2 class="text-primary-emphasis">Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li>
                <strong>Create Blogs:</strong> Users can create a blog with a title and content.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Edit Blogs:</strong> Users can update the title or content of their existing blogs.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Delete Blogs:</strong> Users can delete unwanted posts with a confirmation step.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>View Blogs:</strong> All published blogs are displayed in a clean, responsive layout.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Contact:</strong> Visitors can send messages through a dedicated Contact Me page.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <hr>

    <!-- Author Section -->
    <section class="my-4">
        <h2 class="text-primary-emphasis">About the Project</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>Dipayan Mandal is the visionary behind QuickBlog. With a passion for web development and a knack for creating intuitive interfaces, Dipayan has brought this project to life with the help of Simran Das who has helped in designing the front-end.</p>
                <p>The technologies used in the Project are following</p>
                <ul class="d-flex list-unstyled">
                    <li class="">HTML</li>
                    <li class="ms-3">CSS</li>
                    <li class="ms-3">JS</li>
                    <li class="ms-3">EJS</li>
                    <li class="ms-3">NODE</li>
                    <li class="ms-3">EXPRESS</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <hr>

    <!-- Navigation Section -->
